description: Ever frustrated which place to get pizza? The Prophet of Pizza will choose the right pizza place for you. Simply give the Prophet two choices, and it will choose the right place for you.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Prophet of Pizza if I should choose Pizza Hut or Pizza Haven.
Pizza Hut or Pizza Haven, which one?
Decide if I should choose Pizza Hut or Pizza Haven.
name: Prophet of Pizza
shortDescription: The Prophet of Pizza will choose the right pizza place for you.
